title: What It Sounds Like When Kids Speak Like Donald Trump
text: A new video from BuzzFeed shows a young boy reciting quotes that were reportedly spoken by Donald Trump. While we're certainly not encouraging kids to curse, it is eye-opening to see how Trump's words sound in another context...
